These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Color: grey, amber, ivory, yellow
House: ranch-style, art-deco, gothic-revival, townhouse
1. House:art-deco is on the left of House:ranch-style##1
2. Color:grey == House:townhouse##1
3. House:gothic-revival is on the right of House:ranch-style##1
4. Color:amber is on the left of House:townhouse##1
5. Color:yellow is on the left of House:ranch-style##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | yellow | ivory | amber | grey   |
| House   | art-deco  | ranch-style     | gothic-revival   | townhouse |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Cigar: chaman, havana, game, fonseca
Food: plum, watermelon, blueberry, pepper
1. Cigar:fonseca == Food:watermelon##1
2. Cigar:chaman is on the far right##1
3. Cigar:havana is on the right of Cigar:fonseca##1
4. Cigar:fonseca is on the right of Food:blueberry##1
5. Food:watermelon is on the left of Food:plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | game | fonseca | havana | chaman    |
| Food   | blueberry    | watermelon      | plum | pepper |

