.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Transport: bike, subway, taxi, van
Pet: ferret, goat, hedgehog, fish
1. Pet:hedgehog is on the left of Pet:fish##1
2. Transport:bike == Pet:ferret##1
3. Pet:goat is on the far right##1
4. Pet:fish is on the right of Transport:van##1
5. Transport:taxi is on the left of Pet:goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | bike | van | taxi   | subway |
| Pet   | ferret   | hedgehog | fish | goat         |

