.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Sport: skiing, surfing, swimming, water-polo
Job: dancer, freelancer, dressmaker, engineer
1. Job:dancer is on the left of Sport:surfing##1
2. Job:freelancer is on the left of Sport:water-polo##1
3. Sport:skiing is on the left of Sport:swimming##1
4. Sport:water-polo == Job:engineer##1
5. Job:dancer is on the left of Sport:surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skiing | swimming | surfing | water-polo   |
| Job     | dressmaker  | dancer    | freelancer       | engineer |

 